description: PENTHOUSE living! 2Bed 2Bath w/2 GARAGE PARKING SPACES, direct elevator access, private roof deck w/sweeping views, plus 270 degree private, wrap-around balcony. This condo is a special offering. 2019 construction, boutique building with only 6 units, in a premier South Boston location. Located within close proximity to Seaport, Fort Point & Downtown Boston, three blocks to the Red Line, and endless dining & entertainment options. The unit offers a spacious and open layout that has loads of natural light. The open floor plan between the sleek kitchen and spacious living room are great for entertaining. The modern kitchen features quartz counters, Thermador appliances, + 4 bar seats. The living room has a gas fireplace and extends outdoors via sliding doors out to your extensive balcony. Both bedrooms are king-sized. The primary suite offers a large walk-in closet, spa-like bathroom w/steam shower, and direct access to your balcony. Laundry in unit, Central AC, & Sonos surround sound.
